%section.primary
  %h2 Services
  %h3 We love working on both new startup ideas as well as existing large application codebases. While we all enjoy experimenting with new technologies and ideas, our core services here reflect our <strong>core expertise</strong>.

  %ul
    - @services.each do |service|
      %li{:class => class_for_service(service)}
        .stretch-small-offset
          .service-title          
            = service.title
          .service-description
            = service.description.html_safe

